		"description": "<p>You tap into your innate fey lineage to help get you out of a tight spot. As a bonus action, you disappear in a cloud of glitter and immediately teleport to an unoccupied square you can see within 15 feet. Creatures within 5 feet of you when you activate this ability must succeed on a DC 12 Constitution saving throw or become dazzled until the start of your next turn. Once you have used this ability, you may not do so again until you complete a long rest.</p>",
